+<?php
+/**
+ * Tests for Issue #2370 — Row and column visibility toggles for manual tables.
+ *
+ * Red-phase (TDD): tests that must fail until Task 3 ships the implementation.
+ *
+ * Coverage:
+ *   T1  Row round-trip: replace_rows saves _tc_hidden flag; get_rows returns it intact.
+ *       PASSES today (TC_Manual_Rows_Service stores row_json as-is — regression guard).
+ *   T2  Source pin: save_manual_rows row sanitizer whitelists _tc_hidden so the flag
+ *       survives the known_keys guard in class-tc-ajax.php.
+ *       FAILS today: _tc_hidden is not in the whitelist, so it is silently dropped.
+ *   T3  TC_Manual_Rows_Service::filter_visible_rows exists and filters out _tc_hidden rows.
+ *       FAILS today: method does not exist yet.
+ *   T4  filter_visible_rows keeps visible rows intact.
+ *       FAILS today: method does not exist yet.
+ *   T5  TC_Manual_Rows_Service::filter_visible_columns exists and strips hidden column keys.
+ *       FAILS today: method does not exist yet.
+ *   T6  Rendered HTML excludes cell data for hidden column.
+ *       FAILS today: no filter is applied to column_keys before render.
+ *   T7  Source-level pin: render_manual_source_table source contains _tc_hidden filter call.
+ *       FAILS today: the filter call has not been written.
+ *   T8  Source-level pin: render_manual_source_table source skips columns with hidden true.
+ *       FAILS today: the filter call has not been written.
+ *
+ * @since 8.1.0 (#2370)
+ */
+
